  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\">\n<p>The <a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/communities/Q29tbXVuaXR5LTM1MzQ=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Japanese Beginner Course Community</strong></a> is exclusively for students of this course, it’s a great place to connect with others who are studying the same course as you and also interact with course teachers.</p>\n<p>If you have any questions on the lessons or just want to practice what you've learned, share study tips or just chat with other students, the community is a great resource for you to use.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/communities/Q29tbXVuaXR5LTM1MzQ=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/92f/98f/9ca/Join_the_community.png\" style=\"width: 300px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib fr-fil\" srcset=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/92f/98f/9ca/Join_the_community.png?width=1920 1x, https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/92f/98f/9ca/Join_the_community.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=2 2x, https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/92f/98f/9ca/Join_the_community.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=3 3x\"></a></p>\n</div>",
